  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Faceless Stalker (Ugothol)",
      "sources": [
        {
          "errata": {
            "alt": "1.1",
            "aonid": 221,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "1.1",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "link": {
            "alt": "Monster Core pg. 12",
            "aonid": 221,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 12",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 12,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Among the subtler of the alghollthu creations were the ugothols\u2014also known as faceless stalkers. These twisted beings used shapeshifting to infiltrate settlements and assassinate key targets. They sowed discord and replaced leaders, causing unwanted organizations to implode and bothersome people to lose face and eventually disappear.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
